evolve. Always, though, the mission has still

03:28.589 --> 03:32.877
remained the teaching, the research, and the 
service. In your opinion, has that changed

03:33.358 --> 03:42.614
drastically in focus from the Hubert era to the 
Corrigan era or in between? No, I don't think it's

03:42.654 --> 03:45.860
changed. Our emphasis on the preparation of 
teachers still has always been there.

