Search and service has been carried on in many 
different ways. There was a laboratory for human

04:04.553 --> 04:15.364
learning in the Department of Education and 
Psychology which moved over to the Department of

04:04.553 --> 04:15.364
Psychology. There was a human learning 
laboratory which was and still is over in the of

04:25.762 --> 04:27.304
health and physical education. Of course, that 
emphasis was on physical performance instead of

04:28.465 --> 04:38.337
intellectual performance of students. I don't

04:38.897 --> 04:42.982
know what else. Now, go ahead. OK. One of the things 
that I have been talking about with different

04:43.583 --> 04:54.756
department people is how this growth and these 
changes have affected your ability to work with

04:43.583 --> 04:54.756
students. In graduate programs, it's not as 
pronounced as it is in the undergraduate level as

04:54.989 --> 05:05.061
far as the growth, because this department has 
been pretty stable as far as growth, right? I mean,

05:05.121 --> 05:09.907
there's a limit to the growth here in this 
department, whereas there is not that in some

05:05.121 --> 05:09.907
others. Well, within this department now, when 
