professors preparing people to be special

05:24.048 --> 05:38.610
education

05:24.048 --> 05:38.610
chief counselors and school counselors. Later 
they added school psychologists to the

05:40.092 --> 05:52.992
preparation, but the preparation of school 
counselors has decreased over the years.

05:53.613 --> 05:58.858
probably less than 10% of our department is 
concerned with preparation of school

05:53.613 --> 05:58.858
counselors. And we are now concerned with the 
preparation of school psychologists, special

05:59.579 --> 06:20.278
education teachers, and independently 
practicing psychologists and researchers at the

05:59.579 --> 06:20.278
PhD level.

