06:38.770 --> 06:43.656
people had joint appointments between 
curriculum instruction and educational

06:38.770 --> 06:43.656
psychology. We now have joint appointments with 
the Student Counseling Service and the

06:48.187 --> 06:56.979
Department of Educational Psychology. And we now 
