professors. Some that are working in the 
counseling? They're working full-time in the

07:14.304 --> 07:17.988
student counseling service, but they teach a 
course for us. Oh, I see. OK. And likewise, with a

07:18.949 --> 07:26.438
couple of local psychiatrists who are listed as 
adjunct professors in the department. We've

07:26.538 --> 07:27.980
never had that before. And we now have that where 
we'll have people off campus doing work with

07:29.201 --> 07:39.793
campus in terms of research and service.

07:40.786 --> 07:48.375
If you're talking about the department also, then 
