07:58.266 --> 08:01.790
the seventh floor in connection with the 
department. This is in effect a teaching

08:02.511 --> 08:09.679
laboratory, but one which takes referrals from 
physicians and counselors and psychologists and

08:10.216 --> 08:20.531
progression workers within 150 or 200 miles of 
